24:08.648 --> 24:10.019
[ENGINE REVS]

24:10.019 --> 24:11.581
Devil: HEY,
YOU WANT A RIDE?

24:11.581 --> 24:14.624
OH, JUST LEAVE ME ALONE!

24:14.624 --> 24:15.855
AW, COME ON. HOP IN.

24:15.855 --> 24:17.657
I WANT YOU TO FEEL
THE V8 IN THIS BABY.

24:17.657 --> 24:19.128
YEAH, WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA WANT IN RETURN?

24:19.128 --> 24:20.860
DO I HAVE TO SIGN
A CONTRACT?

24:20.860 --> 24:21.961
HEH HEH. YOU KNOW, SAM...

24:21.961 --> 24:24.934
SARCASM IS THE LOWEST FORM
OF SOCIAL DISCOURSE.

24:24.934 --> 24:28.137
