CHAMP?

24:29.739 --> 24:31.971
HOW ABOUT YOU--
YOU OWN MY SOUL?

24:31.971 --> 24:33.503
YOU WON'T LET ME
TAKE ANY VACATIONS.

24:33.503 --> 24:37.076
