YOU GAVE MY PARENTS
JUST TURNED TO DUST!

24:37.076 --> 24:38.207
FORGET ABOUT
THE CONTRACT.

24:38.207 --> 24:40.580
NO. NO, I WANT TO SEE IT.

24:40.580 --> 24:41.080
BUT WHY?

24:41.080 --> 24:43.583
BECAUSE I WANT TO KNOW
MY RIGHTS.

24:43.583 --> 24:46.956
OH, THAT'S EASY.
