24:47.957 --> 24:49.959
[CAR HORN HONKS]

24:49.959 --> 24:52.121
GO AROUND!
[HORN HONKS]

24:53.593 --> 24:55.665
Man: GO TO HELL, JERK!

24:55.665 --> 24:58.868
