25:05.204 --> 25:06.806
SO I'M--I'M A SLAVE.

25:06.806 --> 25:09.278
AND I CATCH ONE SOUL
AFTER ANOTHER
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

25:09.278 --> 25:11.641
