CAN I HELP YOU?

25:35.835 --> 25:37.837
NO.

25:37.837 --> 25:39.969
HI! CAN I HELP YOU?

25:39.969 --> 25:42.011
NO.

25:45.014 --> 25:48.317
HI, I'M ANDI.
CAN I HELP YOU?

25:49.879 --> 25:51.150
