A DRIVEWAY SEALANT
SEMINAR AT LUNCH, TED,

26:46.235 --> 26:49.008
BASIC INFORMATION
ON INSTALLATION,

26:49.008 --> 26:50.009
MAINTENANCE,
WHAT HAVE YOU.

26:50.009 --> 26:52.011
AND I KNOW THAT YOU'VE
BEEN TRYING TO BEEF UP

26:52.011 --> 26:54.043
