DEPARTMENT FOR
QUITE SOME TIME,

26:54.043 --> 26:55.614
AS WELL AS OUR KNOWLEDGE
OF DRIVEWAY SEALANTS,

26:55.614 --> 26:59.719
SO WE THOUGHT WE'D
GO OVER THERE AND BONE
UP ON DRIVEWAY SEALANT.

26:59.719 --> 27:00.349
THAT'S THAT.

27:00.349 --> 27:03.252
YOU KNOW WHAT, GUYS?
