AND UTTER IDIOT.

27:12.301 --> 27:14.804
HMM?

27:14.804 --> 27:16.005
AHEM.

27:16.005 --> 27:16.936
HMM.

27:16.936 --> 27:19.008
GUYS, SERIOUSLY.
DRIVEWAY SEALANT?

