THINK I'M JUST GONNA LET YOU
BLOW OFF WORK TO GO TO
A MAGIC SHOW WITH ANDI?

27:22.972 --> 27:25.845
HEH! MAGIC SHOW.
PLEASE!

27:25.845 --> 27:28.918
WAIT, WAIT!
TED, HOW DO YOU KNOW ABOUT
A MAGIC SHOW WITH ANDI?

27:28.918 --> 27:29.819
