REALLY, REALLY TAN...

27:34.383 --> 27:38.387
YOU KNOW WHAT, SAM?
I'M NOT REALLY IN THE HABIT
OF CHECKING OTHER MEN OUT.

27:38.387 --> 27:40.790
UNLIKE SOME PEOPLE I KNOW.

27:40.790 --> 27:42.061
HUH? OH, SORRY. HEH!

27:42.061 --> 27:45.935
I WAS SO BUSY
CHECKING OUT YOUR ASS,
I MISSED YOUR FUNNY JOKE.

27:45.935 --> 27:47.837
OK, COME ON, COME ON.
LET'S GO.

27:47.837 --> 27:50.800
DID YOU WANT TO
REPEAT IT, OR...

27:51.771 --> 27:55.975
