WHY ARE WE RUNNING?

27:56.976 --> 27:59.779
THE DEVIL'S TRYING
TO SET UP ANDI. LET'S GO.

27:59.779 --> 28:01.711
WAIT, WAIT!
LET ME CATCH MY BREATH!

28:01.711 --> 28:03.682
SAM!
RELAX. HE'LL BE BACK.

28:03.682 --> 28:05.354
WHERE THE HELL'S
THE BIRD?

28:05.354 --> 28:06.816
HE GOT OUT.

28:06.816 --> 28:08.087
[DOVE COOING]

28:08.087 --> 28:09.688
Sam: WHAT? HOW?

28:09.688 --> 28:10.089
WE WERE TALKING.

28:10.089 --> 28:13.923
ALL RIGHT,
JUST CATCH THE BIRD AND
MEET ME AT THE MAGIC SHOW.

28:13.923 --> 28:14.924
COME ON, WINSTON.

28:14.924 --> 28:16.996
COME TO DADDY.
WE HAVE TO GO NOW.

28:16.996 --> 28:18.167
I'LL BRING HIM DOWN.

28:18.167 --> 28:21.901
I WILL CUT YOU
WHERE YOU STAND.

28:24.133 --> 28:27.376
SO WHAT IS IT NOW,
ROOF TAR CLASS?

28:27.376 --> 28:28.477
LOOK, TED...

28:28.477 --> 28:29.979
I'LL WORK THE WEEKEND SHIFT.

28:29.979 --> 28:32.081
I'LL WORK THE NEXT
4 WEEKEND SHIFTS!

28:32.081 --> 28:34.984
I'LL WORK NIGHTS!
HELL, I'LL EVEN
WORK THANKSGIVING!

28:34.984 --> 28:36.245
COME ON!
SERIOUSLY, YOU'D...

28:36.245 --> 28:38.017
YOU'D GIVE UP ALL THAT?

28:38.017 --> 28:39.749
YES. NOW MOVE!

28:39.749 --> 28:41.921
OK THEN.

28:46.355 --> 28:48.798
TED IS GOOD.

29:05.244 --> 29:06.415
[WHISPERING]
Hey, what are you doing?

29:06.415 --> 29:07.977
HEY, WHAT TOOK YOU
SO LONG?

29:07.977 --> 29:09.018
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

29:09.018 --> 29:11.050
I GOT YOUR VOICEMAIL
TO MEET YOU HERE.

29:11.050 --> 29:12.021
VOICEMAIL?
IN MY VOICE?

29:12.021 --> 29:15.224
UM, YEAH? WHAT, YOU DON'T
REMEMBER LEAVING IT?

29:15.224 --> 29:17.787
UH...THAT MESSAGE.
YES, YES.

29:17.787 --> 29:20.329
I DO. UM, SORRY, I HAD
A SMALL STROKE EARLIER.

29:20.329 --> 29:21.460
WE GOTTA GO. LET'S--

29:21.460 --> 29:23.032
NO, NO!
THIS IS KIND OF FUN.

29:23.032 --> 29:26.195
THIS--HE SUCKS!
LET'S GO.

29:26.195 --> 29:29.038
HE'S RIGHT BEHIND ME,
ISN'T HE?

29:29.038 --> 29:31.470
MM-HMM.
I SUCK.

29:31.470 --> 29:32.842
UM...

29:32.842 --> 29:34.073
WHY DON'T YOU
COME UP ONSTAGE

29:34.073 --> 29:35.975
AND LET ME SHOW YOU
SOME REAL MAGIC?

29:35.975 --> 29:39.208
I--I WOULD DO THAT,
BUT WE WERE JUST LEAVING.

29:39.208 --> 29:43.152
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
COME ON, GIVE THIS GUY
SOME ENCOURAGEMENT.

29:43.152 --> 29:44.413
NO, NO! SERIOUSLY, NO.

29:44.413 --> 29:46.415
ANDI, STOP LAUGHING.
WE GOTTA GO.

29:46.415 --> 29:48.087
YOU'RE SUCH A CHICKEN.

29:48.087 --> 29:49.859
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I'LL DO IT.

29:49.859 --> 29:50.860
NO! NO, YOU CAN'T.

29:50.860 --> 29:52.561
WHY NOT? IT'LL BE FUN.
I'LL DO IT.

29:52.561 --> 29:56.065
BECAUSE...
HE ASKED ME FIRST.

29:56.065 --> 29:58.497
RIGHT?
OK.

30:00.830 --> 30:03.873
LET'S DO THIS.

30:16.015 --> 30:17.486
YOU LOOKING FOR SOMETHING?

30:17.486 --> 30:18.147
UM...

30:18.147 --> 30:19.518
THIS ISN'T ENOUGH
TO HOLD YOUR ATTENTION?

30:19.518 --> 30:23.252
UH, NO. MY FRIENDS
ARE SUPPOSED TO
MEET ME HERE,

30:23.252 --> 30:25.394
SO I WAS...
TOUCH IT.

30:25.394 --> 30:26.255
WHAT?

30:26.255 --> 30:29.328
TOUCH THE SWORD.
TELL THEM IT'S REAL.

30:30.559 --> 30:32.001
I DON'T KNOW.

30:32.001 --> 30:33.832
