30:33.832 --> 30:36.135
HOLD IT. IT'S REAL.

30:36.135 --> 30:37.836
YEAH, THAT'S, UH...

30:37.836 --> 30:42.241
THAT'S SOME PRETTY GOOD
ACTION RIGHT THERE. YEAH.

30:42.241 --> 30:45.144
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
LOOKS LIKE OUR VOLUNTEER'S

30:45.144 --> 30:46.916
CONTRACTED A CASE
OF STAGE FRIGHT.

30:46.916 --> 30:49.448
WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

30:52.451 --> 30:54.383
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!

30:54.383 --> 30:57.256
GIVE ME BACK MY SWORD.

30:57.256 --> 31:00.359
YOU NEED IT, DON'T YOU?

31:00.960 --> 31:02.491
YOU HAVE NO POWER
WITHOUT IT.

31:02.491 --> 31:03.993
WHAT ARE YOU, A DEMON?

31:03.993 --> 31:06.435
NO, I'M JUST THE GUY
SENDING YOU BACK TO HELL.

31:06.435 --> 31:10.139
JUST AS SOON AS
MY FRIENDS SHOW UP.

31:10.139 --> 31:13.072
UH! I'M NOT GONNA LET YOU
KILL ANYMORE PEOPLE!

31:13.072 --> 31:16.605
THOSE YOKELS OUT THERE
GET WHAT THEY DESERVE.

31:16.605 --> 31:18.377
I GIVE THEM PURE MAGIC,

31:18.377 --> 31:21.110
AND THEY RESPOND
LIKE A BUNCH OF
SLACK-JAWED CATTLE.

31:21.110 --> 31:24.613
YEAH, WELL, MAYBE
THEY RESPOND THAT WAY BECAUSE
YOU'RE SUCH A TOTAL DICKWAD.

31:24.613 --> 31:27.156
YOU HAVE NO IDEA WHAT
I WENT THROUGH IN HELL,

31:27.156 --> 31:30.089
WHAT I FEELS LIKE
TO BE IMPALED ON A SWORD

31:30.089 --> 31:30.519
FOR DECADES ON END.

31:30.519 --> 31:34.363
YEAH, WELL, GET USED TO IT,
BECAUSE YOU'RE GOING BACK.

31:35.164 --> 31:37.666
AAH! UNH!

31:37.666 --> 31:39.628
AAH!

31:42.101 --> 31:43.933
AAH!

31:43.933 --> 31:45.604
GAH!

31:45.604 --> 31:47.106
AAH!

31:47.106 --> 31:49.478
[GRUNTING]

31:53.382 --> 31:55.114
AAH!

32:19.238 --> 32:22.141
WHOA!

32:25.544 --> 32:28.577
AAH! [GRUNTING]

32:37.026 --> 32:39.989
OOH! WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

32:50.439 --> 32:52.341
[GRUNTS]

32:58.007 --> 32:59.048
SAM! YOU ALL RIGHT?

32:59.048 --> 33:00.979
NO, NO!
HE'S RIGHT BEHIND ME!

33:00.979 --> 33:03.212
GIVE ME THE VESSEL.
GIVE ME THE VESSEL.

33:03.212 --> 33:04.083
Ben: HERE.

33:04.083 --> 33:06.085
Sock: WAVE IT AROUND!
WAVE IT AROUND!

33:06.085 --> 33:08.157
[ALL TALKING AT ONCE]

33:08.157 --> 33:09.588
Sam: YOU STUPID BIRD,
COME ON!

33:09.588 --> 33:11.120
COME ON! COME ON!
GO, GO!

33:11.120 --> 33:12.721
COME ON, WINSTON!
GO, WINSTON!

33:12.721 --> 33:15.764
COME ON, COME ON.
COME ON, WINSTON.

33:15.764 --> 33:17.266
IT'S SAD. SO STUPID,

33:17.266 --> 33:21.030
YOU CAN'T
EVEN FIGURE OUT
THE SIMPLEST OF TRICKS.

33:21.030 --> 33:22.000
HUH? TRICKS?

33:22.000 --> 33:25.074
TRICKS. THAT'S IT!
THAT'S IT!

33:27.176 --> 33:30.109
SAM, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING, SAM?

33:32.041 --> 33:34.783
UH, TA DA?

33:36.715 --> 33:39.318
[BIRD CALLING]

33:42.121 --> 33:43.092
WINSTON?

33:43.092 --> 33:44.553
[BIRD CALLING]

33:44.553 --> 33:46.095
[WINGS BEATING]

33:46.095 --> 33:47.256
[ALL SHOUTING]

33:47.256 --> 33:50.059
AAH!

34:04.313 --> 34:05.174
THAT, MY FRIEND...

34:05.174 --> 34:07.316
WAS SOME FINE HELL SUCKING.

34:07.316 --> 34:08.347
COME ON.

34:08.347 --> 34:10.279
WINSTON? WHA--

34:10.279 --> 34:12.081
OH, MAN!

34:12.081 --> 34:13.422
[EXHALES]

34:13.422 --> 34:15.824
[SOCK LAUGHING]

34:15.824 --> 34:17.356
HA HA HA HA!

34:17.356 --> 34:18.687
AW.
MAN.

34:18.687 --> 34:21.090
AW, THAT WAS AWESOME.

34:22.831 --> 34:25.234
Sock: MM-MMM.

34:25.234 --> 34:27.065
HI, GLADYS.

34:27.065 --> 34:29.368
YOU ARE LOOKING...
[GRUNTS] TODAY!

34:29.368 --> 34:32.401
PLACE THE VESSEL
ON THE MAT.

34:32.401 --> 34:34.303
WHOA. IT'S GONNA BE
KIND OF DIFFICULT

34:34.303 --> 34:37.476
WITH ALL THAT SEXUAL
TENSION PUSHING BACK.

34:38.307 --> 34:40.679
YOU READY?

34:42.211 --> 34:43.282
YEAH.

34:43.282 --> 34:45.554
OH, I--CAN I HAVE
A MOMENT?

34:45.554 --> 34:48.086
YEAH.
YEAH.

34:48.587 --> 34:50.819
WINSTON...

34:52.261 --> 34:54.423
YOU'RE ONE
FREAKY ASS BIRD

34:54.423 --> 34:55.724
WHO SCARED THE CRAP
OUT OF ME,

34:55.724 --> 34:59.428
AND NOW I CAN'T
BE COMFORTABLE
AROUND BIRDS EVER AGAIN.

34:59.428 --> 35:02.171
I HOPE YOU KNOW THAT.

35:04.673 --> 35:05.874
OK.

35:05.874 --> 35:06.635
ALL RIGHT.

35:06.635 --> 35:08.807
COOL.
IT'S COOL.

35:08.807 --> 35:10.779
OK.

35:10.779 --> 35:12.281
THANK YOU, GLADYS.

35:12.281 --> 35:13.682
OH, I'M SORRY.

35:13.682 --> 35:15.714
THESE ARE HIS FAVORITE.

35:15.714 --> 35:18.417
OK, NOW I'M DONE.

35:27.826 --> 35:30.499
Andi: SO WHAT DID
HAPPEN TO YOU?

35:30.499 --> 35:33.232
YEAH, THAT WAS A HELL
OF A MAGIC TRICK.

35:33.232 --> 35:34.803
HE MADE YOU BOTH
DISAPPEAR.

35:34.803 --> 35:37.406
WHY DID YOU
RUN OFF THE STAGE?

35:37.406 --> 35:39.438
YEAH, I, UM...

35:39.438 --> 35:41.310
I ATE A BAD HOTDOG, SO--

35:41.310 --> 35:43.572
OOH. YEAH, WELL...

35:43.572 --> 35:44.873
YOU BETTER MAN UP
FOR THIS WEEKEND

35:44.873 --> 35:48.177
BECAUSE WE HAVE
A LONG TRIP AND
LIMITED BATHROOM STOPS.

35:48.177 --> 35:51.820
RIGHT, YES.
UM, ABOUT THAT...

35:51.820 --> 35:54.653
I...I CAN'T GO.

35:54.653 --> 35:56.355
[SCOFFS] WHAT?

35:56.355 --> 35:58.156
ARE YOU THAT SICK?

35:58.156 --> 35:58.927
NO, NO, NO.

35:58.927 --> 36:00.189
UM...I'M WORKING.

36:00.189 --> 36:03.532
I TOLD TED THAT I'D WORK
THE NEXT 4 WEEKEND SHIFTS.

36:03.532 --> 36:05.564
WHAT? WHY WOULD YOU
SAY THAT?

36:05.564 --> 36:08.437
I MEAN, YOU KNEW WE WERE
GOING AWAY THIS WEEKEND.

36:08.437 --> 36:09.298
DON'T BE MAD. I--

36:09.298 --> 36:12.441
NO, I'M NOT MAD.
I'M JUST...I'M CONFUSED.

36:12.441 --> 36:13.902
I MEAN, IF YOU DIDN'T
WANT TO GO WITH ME,

36:13.902 --> 36:15.474
WHY WOULDN'T YOU
JUST SAY THAT,

36:15.474 --> 36:18.347
AND WHY SADDLE YOURSELF
WITH WEEKEND SHIFTS?

36:19.648 --> 36:21.850
TH--THAT IS
AN EXCELLENT QUESTION.

36:21.850 --> 36:22.811
OK, THEN ANSWER IT.

36:22.811 --> 36:24.583
THAT I CAN'T--
I CAN'T ANSWER.

36:24.583 --> 36:26.184
IT'S HARD TO EXPLAIN,
ALL RIGHT?

36:26.184 --> 36:28.787
I--I TRIED,
BUT TED WOULDN'T LET ME.

36:28.787 --> 36:30.289
IT'S NOT THAT
I DIDN'T WANT TO--

36:30.289 --> 36:31.890
OK, YOU KNOW WHAT?
I TAKE IT BACK.

36:31.890 --> 36:33.322
I AM MAD.

36:33.322 --> 36:33.962
WAIT, ANDI, HOLD ON!

36:33.962 --> 36:36.695
YOU KNOW WHAT?
WE COULD'VE HAD A REALLY
GREAT WEEKEND, SAM.

36:36.695 --> 36:40.599
AND THEN YOU HAD TO GET
ALL CAUGHT UP IN YOUR
HEAD AND MAKE IT WEIRD.

36:40.599 --> 36:41.870
NO! I DON'T THINK
IT'S WEIRD.

36:41.870 --> 36:43.972
IT'S THE OPPOSITE.
IT'S NOT WEIRD.

36:43.972 --> 36:45.374
YES, IT FEELS WEIRD.

36:45.374 --> 36:47.576
LISTEN, YOU'RE LIKE
MY BEST FRIEND, OK?

36:47.576 --> 36:50.379
I REALLY DON'T WANT
THINGS TO CHANGE.

36:50.379 --> 36:51.640
AND THEY WON'T!

36:51.640 --> 36:53.782
WE--WE'RE--WE ARE FRIENDS.

36:53.782 --> 36:54.243
YEAH.

36:54.243 --> 36:58.487
JUST FRIENDS THAT
CAN'T SPEND TIME
ALONE TOGETHER, HUH?

36:58.947 --> 37:00.289
NEVER MIND.

37:00.289 --> 37:01.219
NEVER MIND.

37:01.219 --> 37:04.893
LISTEN, I'LL BRING YOU
BACK A PROGRAM, OK?

37:07.696 --> 37:09.958
[SIGHS]

37:16.435 --> 37:18.267
AH, DRINKING ALONE.

37:18.267 --> 37:20.469
THAT'S A SLIPPERY SLOPE.

37:20.469 --> 37:21.239
HEH HEH.

37:21.239 --> 37:22.641
I DON'T HAVE
MUCH ELSE TO DO.

37:22.641 --> 37:26.575
AH. I'LL HAVE A CRANBERRY
AND SODA, MY GOOD WOMAN.

37:26.575 --> 37:29.017
OH, I NEVER DRINK
WHILE I WORK.

37:29.017 --> 37:30.018
CLOUDS THE MIND.

37:30.018 --> 37:33.652
MAYBE IF YOU DRANK,
YOU'D BE LESS OF A DICK.

37:33.652 --> 37:35.954
HMM, YEAH.

37:35.954 --> 37:37.986
HEH HEH! OH, BUDDY.

37:37.986 --> 37:40.889
YOU'VE WORKED HARD,
SACRIFICED.

37:40.889 --> 37:43.932
I REALLY APPRECIATE THAT.

37:45.894 --> 37:47.296
YOU KNOW WHAT?

37:47.296 --> 37:48.967
YOU CAN TAKE
THE WEEKEND OFF.

37:48.967 --> 37:50.669
GO TO YOUR LITTLE CONCERT.

37:50.669 --> 37:53.001
DROP SOME ECSTASY,
WHATEVER YOU WANT.

37:53.001 --> 37:54.573
I WORK THIS WEEKEND.

37:54.573 --> 37:57.946
I WORK THE NEXT 4
WEEKENDS BECAUSE OF YOU.

37:57.946 --> 37:59.007
WHAT DID I DO?

37:59.007 --> 38:00.749
YOU PUT ANDI IN DANGER.

38:00.749 --> 38:02.411
OH.

38:02.411 --> 38:05.784
YEAH, RIGHT.
I DID, DIDN'T I?

38:06.415 --> 38:08.957
[SIGHS]

38:08.957 --> 38:10.559
[EXHALES]

38:10.559 --> 38:12.691
WELL, THIS REALLY SUCKS.

38:12.691 --> 38:14.663
CAN'T GO ON YOUR TRIP.

38:14.663 --> 38:16.064
YOU DON'T GET THE GIRL.

38:16.064 --> 38:19.328
YOU EXPECT ME TO BELIEVE
YOU FEEL BAD FOR ME? WHAT?

38:19.328 --> 38:20.799
I DO!
NO, YOU DON'T.

38:20.799 --> 38:22.771
I DO, I DO.
I FEEL TERRIBLE.

38:22.771 --> 38:25.003
I FEEL CRAPPY.
I FEEL AWFUL.

38:25.003 --> 38:25.504
[SCOFFS]

38:25.504 --> 38:30.509
YOU SURE THERE'S
NOTHING I CAN DO
TO MAKE IT UP TO YOU?

38:32.941 --> 38:34.543
I WANT THE CONTRACT.

38:34.543 --> 38:37.846
WHAT DO YOU HAVE?
A DEATH WISH?

38:37.846 --> 38:40.489
WELL, I REALIZED
IF ANYTHING'S
GONNA KILL ME,

38:40.489 --> 38:44.653
IT'S GONNA BE SOME
PSYCHO ESCAPED SOUL
FROM HELL, NOT YOU.

38:44.653 --> 38:48.897
BECAUSE...YOU NEED ME.

38:49.928 --> 38:53.862
AND I--
I NEED THAT CONTRACT.

38:58.036 --> 38:59.037
HEH HEH!

38:59.037 --> 39:02.371
SEE, WHAT IS IT
ABOUT YOU, SAMMY?

39:02.371 --> 39:05.043
HUH? I JUST CAN'T SAY NO.

39:05.043 --> 39:08.677
ALL RIGHT, I'LL TALK
TO THE GUYS DOWNSTAIRS

39:08.677 --> 39:10.879
AND SEE IF THEY CAN
DIG UP A DRAFT, ALL RIGHT?

39:10.879 --> 39:15.454
FILING SYSTEM
IN THE ABYSS IS SHABBY,
AS YOU MIGHT EXPECT,

39:15.454 --> 39:18.056
BUT I'LL PUT IN A REQUEST.

39:18.056 --> 39:20.058
OK? FAIR ENOUGH?

39:20.058 --> 39:21.930
YES. THANK YOU.

39:21.930 --> 39:23.862
YEAH, WELL...

39:23.862 --> 39:25.363
AHEM. WHAT THE HECK.

39:25.363 --> 39:28.096
I'LL HAVE
WHAT HE'S HAVING.

39:28.096 --> 39:30.969
YOU KNOW THE ONE
BRIGHT SIDE OF ALL THIS?

39:30.969 --> 39:33.802
NOW YOU KNOW
THAT ANDI'S INTO YOU.

39:33.802 --> 39:35.904
NO, SHE ALMOST
BIT MY HEAD OFF.

39:35.904 --> 39:36.475
EXACTLY.

39:36.475 --> 39:40.108
THE LADY DOTH PROTEST
TOO MUCH, METHINKS.

39:40.879 --> 39:41.910
THANKS.

39:41.910 --> 39:44.553
DO YOU--
DO YOU REALLY THINK SO?

39:44.553 --> 39:45.514
TRUST ME, BUDDY.

39:45.514 --> 39:49.017
I DO KNOW A THING OR TWO
ABOUT THE HUMAN ANIMAL.
